    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-green);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">2. Z-Score Mean Reversion Sinyal Uretimi</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>MeanReversionSignalGenerator.cs</code>, <code>ZScoreCalculator.cs</code></p>

        <p>
            Sistem, <strong>Z-Score tabanli mean reversion</strong> stratejisi kullanir. 1m mum verilerinden 5 dakikalik blok
            getiriler hesaplanir, bu getirilerin Z-Score'u bulunur. Z-Score esik degeri (1.8) astiginda contrarian sinyal uretilir:
            yuksek Z-Score (overbought) = Down sinyal, dusuk Z-Score (oversold) = Up sinyal.
        </p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Sinyal Uretim Katmanlari</h3>
        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Katman</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                    <th>Parametre</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Z-Score</strong></td>
                    <td>1m mumlardan 5 dakikalik blok getiriler hesaplanir, son 120 dakikalik pencere uzerinden Z-Score bulunur</td>
                    <td><code>ZScoreThreshold = 1.8</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Indikator Teyidi</strong></td>
                    <td>Contrarian: Down sinyal icin en az 3 bullish indikator, Up sinyal icin en az 3 bearish indikator gerekir</td>
                    <td><code>ConfirmThreshold = 3</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Fair Value</strong></td>
                    <td>Z-Score'dan Normal CDF ile fair value hesaplanir, market price ile karsilastirilarak edge bulunur</td>
                    <td><code>DecayFactor = 0.4</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Rejim Tespiti</strong></td>
                    <td>Parkinson volatilite ile kisa/uzun donem karsilastirilir. Yuksek volatilite rejiminde pozisyon boyutu azaltilir</td>
                    <td><code>Short=60m, Long=720m</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Pozisyon Boyutu</strong></td>
                    <td>Kelly criterion ile optimal pozisyon boyutu hesaplanir, minimum edge kontrolu yapilir</td>
                    <td><code>Kelly fraction</code></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Z-Score Hesaplama (ZScoreCalculator)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// ZScoreCalculator.Compute(candles)
// 1. Son 120 dakikalik pencereden 5'er dakikalik blok getiriler hesapla
// 2. Getirilerin ortalama (mu) ve standart sapmasini (sigma) bul
// 3. Son 5 dakikalik getiriyi hesapla
// 4. Z = (currentReturn - mu) / sigma
// Z > 1.8  → overbought  → DOWN sinyal
// Z &lt; -1.8 → oversold    → UP sinyal
        </pre>
    </div>

