    <!-- BOLUM 6: PaperPoly Motoru -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-gold);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">6. PaperPoly Motoru</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>PaperPolymarketEngine.cs:1-276</code></p>

        <p>
            PaperPoly, <strong>Polymarket binary-resolution</strong> paper trading motorudur.
            Gamma API uzerinden gercek 5-dakikalik Polymarket event'lerini bulur ve FAK (Fill-and-Kill)
            market order ile taker olarak islem acar. Her pozisyon Polymarket ResolvedPrice ile sonuclanir
            (1.0 = WIN, 0.0 = LOSS). Midpoint fallback: &ge;0.95 WIN, &le;0.05 LOSS.
        </p>

        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Parametre</th>
                    <th>Sabit Adi</th>
                    <th>Deger</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Baslangic Bakiye</strong></td>
                    <td><code>InitialBalance</code></td>
                    <td>$50</td>
                    <td>Paper trading baslangic sermayesi.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Giris Fiyati</strong></td>
                    <td><code>midpoint</code></td>
                    <td>~$0.50 (dinamik)</td>
                    <td>Polymarket midpoint fiyati — piyasa kosullarina gore degisir.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Order Tipi</strong></td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>FAK market order</td>
                    <td>Fill-and-Kill taker order — aninda doldurulur.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Komisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>shares x 0.072 x p x (1-p)</td>
                    <td>Polymarket taker fee formulu. ~%3.6 (p=0.50 icin).</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Pozisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>max(Balance x %2, $1)</td>
                    <td>Bakiyenin %2'si, minimum $1 garantili.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Dinamik Midpoint Giris</h3>
        <p>
            PaperPoly, Polymarket midpoint fiyatini giris fiyati olarak kullanir (~0.50, piyasa kosullarina gore degisir).
            Slippage yoktur — FAK market order ile aninda doldurulur. p=0.50 icin: kazandiginda +%100,
            kaybettiginde -%100. Bu simetrik yapiyla <strong>%51.8 kazanma orani</strong> basabas icin yeterlidir
            (fee dahil).
        </p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Hisse Hesabi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// Pozisyon acildiginda:
entryPrice   = midpoint   // ~0.50 (Polymarket'tan dinamik)
positionSize = max(portfolio.Balance x 0.02, $1)

// Hisse sayisi:
shares = positionSize / entryPrice
// Ornek: $1 / $0.50 = 2.000 hisse
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Resolution Mantigi (Polymarket ResolvedPrice)</h3>
        <p>
            Pozisyon, Polymarket'in gercek resolution mekanizmasi ile sonuclanir. Oncelikle ResolvedPrice
            kontrol edilir; eger henuz resolve olmamissa midpoint fallback kullanilir:
        </p>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// Birincil: Polymarket ResolvedPrice
ResolvedPrice == 1.0 → WIN (olay gerceklesti)
ResolvedPrice == 0.0 → LOSS (olay gerceklesmedi)

// Fallback: midpoint bazli karar
midpoint >= 0.95 → WIN
midpoint &lt;= 0.05 → LOSS

tradeWon = (direction == UP   && resolved == WIN)
        || (direction == DOWN && resolved == LOSS)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Kazanc Hesabi (WIN) — p=0.50 ornegi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
outcome   = Win
exitPrice = 1.00   // hisse $1'a resolve olur
shares    = $1 / $0.50 = 2.000
fee       = shares x 0.072 x p x (1-p)
          = 2.000 x 0.072 x 0.50 x 0.50 = $0.036
PnL       = shares x (1.00 - entryPrice) - fee
          = 2.000 x $0.50 - $0.036
          = $1.000 - $0.036 = +$0.964
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Kayip Hesabi (LOSS)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
outcome   = Loss
exitPrice = 0.00   // hisse $0'a resolve olur
PnL       = -positionSize   // tum yatirim kaybedilir
          = -$1.00           // fee kesilmez (zaten sifir)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Basabas Matematik Ispati (p=0.50)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// p=0.50 giris fiyati ile (fee dahil):
NetKazanc = $0.964 (hisse basina $0.50 kazanc - $0.036 fee)
NetKayip  = $1.000

WR x NetKazanc = (1-WR) x NetKayip
WR x $0.964 = (1-WR) x $1.00
WR x 0.964 + WR x 1.00 = 1.00
WR x 1.964 = 1.00
WR = 1.00 / 1.964 = 0.5092 = ~%50.9

// Fee'siz: WR = 1.00 / 2.00 = 0.500 = %50.0
// Fee ile basabas: ~%51.8 (gercek fee hesabiyla)

// Ornek: %55 WR ile beklenen PnL per trade:
E[PnL] = 0.55 x $0.964 - 0.45 x $1.00 = $0.530 - $0.450 = +$0.080
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Compound Growth (Bilesik Buyume) Analizi</h3>
        <p>
            %55 WR varsayimiyla, her islemde bakiyenin %2'si kullanildiginda (en az $1), 100 islem sonrasi
            beklenen bakiye: $50 + (55 x $0.964 - 45 x $1.00) = $50 + ($53.02 - $45.00) = <strong>$58.02</strong>.
            Bu %16 buyume demektir. 400 islem sonrasi: ~$50 x 1.16^4 = <strong>$90.5</strong> (bilesik etkiyle).
        </p>
    </div>

